Don't even think it.

708
00:55:00,047 --> 00:55:01,632
The way it works is this.

709
00:55:01,716 --> 00:55:05,094
If you don't re-up the minutes
on your cell phone before 60 days,

710
00:55:05,178 --> 00:55:08,890
the wireless company recycles the numbers.
That's where I get them.

711
00:55:08,973 --> 00:55:13,478
I put the word out on the street that I'm
buying tossed-off burners, paying $2 a pop.

712
00:55:13,561 --> 00:55:15,605
Street people bring me hundreds.

713
00:55:15,688 --> 00:55:21,152
I bring them here to my niece, shejuices them
up another 200 minutes on a bogus account.

714
00:55:21,235 --> 00:55:25,781
And that automatically extends
the life of the phone for another 60 days.

715
00:55:26,657 --> 00:55:29,118
She charges me 20 on each phone on her end.

716
00:55:29,202 --> 00:55:31,746
I double it or more on
the street to make mine.

717
00:55:31,829 --> 00:55:33,748
So what you saying?

718
00:55:34,332 --> 00:55:37,835
Baby, a standard trac phone with 200,
maybe 400 minutes on it,

719
00:55:37,919 --> 00:55:39,837
gonna run you 150, 200 easy.

720
00:55:39,921 --> 00:55:43,674
I charge you an even 100.
You clear 50 on each phone.

721
00:55:43,758 --> 00:55:46,177
That's if you got receipts.

722
00:55:46,260 --> 00:55:51,516
I gotta show receipts looking like they
from different places, or I can't play.

723
00:55:51,599 --> 00:55:56,312
- Can we accommodate the good man?
- Damn, you know I got the bingo tonight.

724
00:56:08,699 --> 00:56:11,035
Look, I ain't sure you
wanna be around here,

725
00:56:11,118 --> 00:56:14,163
and I'm damn sure
we're getting tired of having you.

726
00:56:14,247 --> 00:56:17,708
I don't wanna be
around no bunch of cocksucking faggots.

727
00:56:17,792 --> 00:56:22,004
But I won't stop coming till I run up on
Omar. You might want to get the word out.

728
00:56:22,088 --> 00:56:25,716
- For the last time, I don't know him.
- Then I'm back tomorrow.

729
00:56:51,033 --> 00:56:53,035
Maybe I can help you?

730
00:56:57,540 --> 00:56:59,500
I don't doubt it for a minute.

